Document: OpenXRSpatialComponentParentList
Path: godot/classes/class_openxrspatialcomponentparentlist.rst
Summary: Method to retrieve parent entity RID by index in an OpenXR spatial component parent list

Method: get_parent(index: int) → RID const
Returns the RID for the parent entity at the specified index in the spatial component parent list. This const method allows querying parent relationships without modifying the list structure. The index parameter must be a valid integer within the bounds of the list.